						<span class="categories">Filed under <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/gold/" rel="category tag">Gold</a></span>
						<span class="tags">Tagged with <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/germany/" rel="tag">germany</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/gold-2/" rel="tag">GOLD</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/piigs/" rel="tag">PIIGS</a></span>					</p>
				</div>

